```java
rule "Control Coffee Maker Based on User Occupancy"
when
    Member of gUserStatus changed   
then
    if (gUserStatus.statesContain(Situation_Away) || gUserStatus.statesContain(Situation_Vacation)) {
        Coffee_Maker.sendCommand(OFF)
    } else {
        Coffee_Maker.sendCommand(ON)
    }
end
```